NK016(ma)006:0: na rag dong sprugs kyi cho ga 'khor ba kun
NK016(ma)006:1: sgrol gyi zur 'debs lhan thabs ngo mtshar rin chen
NK016(ma)006:2: phreng ba zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK016(ma)006:3: bla ma dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK016(ma)006:4: 'dir zhi khro dam pa rigs brgya'i sgrub thabs na
NK016(ma)006:5: rag dong sprugs 'khor ba kun sgrol gyi cho ga'i
NK016(ma)006:6: lhan thabs cung zad spros pa ngo mtshar rin chen
NK016(ma)006:7: phreng ba zhes bya ba 'di la don gsum /
NK016(ma)006:9: dzapa bzlas kyi bcu cha brtsi tshul /
NK016(ma)006:12: phyag rgya'i mchod pa'i skabs su rgyas par 'dod na
NK016(ma)006:13: dkyil 'khor 'di'i lha grangs dang mnyam pa'i phyag rgya'i
NK016(ma)006:14: mchod pa spros chog par gsungs pas /
NK016(ma)006:15: de'i phyir du cho ga shin tu rgyas pa la
NK016(ma)006:16: mos pa dag gi bzhed pa skong phyir du sgyu
NK016(ma)006:17: 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhi ba 'bring po dang /
NK016(ma)006:18: khro bo bsdus pa'i las gzhung gnyis la brten nas cung zad 'bri ba la gnyis /
NK016(ma)006:21: dang po zhi ba'i phyag rgyala'ang spyi dang khyad bar gnyis las /
NK016(ma)006:23: thabs dang shes rab kyi phyag rgya rdo rje dang dril bu bzung la /
NK016(ma)006:24: lag pa g.yas kyi sor mo'i bre kha lnga la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor re re /
NK016(ma)006:25: de rnams kyi steng du h'u s+w+aa +aam h+aa /
NK016(ma)006:26: g.yon gyi sor mo'i bre kha lnga la zla ba'i dkyil 'khor re re /
NK016(ma)006:27: de dag gi steng du m+aum l+aam m+aam b+aam t+aam rnams kyis mtshan par gyur /
NK016(ma)006:28: h+aum sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK016(ma)006:29: thams cad byang chub mchog gi rgya //
NK016(ma)006:30: gsang ba de nyid nges pa yi //
NK016(ma)006:32: mi bskyod nyi ma'i dkyil yi ge //
NK016(ma)006:33: rin chen zla ba'i dkyil yi ge //
NK016(ma)006:34: lnga gnyis zung du sprad pa las //
NK016(ma)006:35: sbyor ba'i phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK016(ma)006:36: dang m+aum gnyis rtse sbyar te //
NK016(ma)006:37: 'bru brgyad bsnol nas rtse sprad pa //
NK016(ma)006:38: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK016(ma)006:39: bde ba chen po sbyin pa'i rgya //
NK016(ma)006:41: dkyil 'khor kun gyi khyab bdag che //
NK016(ma)006:42: kun bzang mnyam gzhag ye shes 'phro //
NK016(ma)006:44: yum ni dmigs med chos kyi dbyings //
NK016(ma)006:46: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta a /
NK016(ma)006:47: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK016(ma)006:48: h'u sgreng rtse mo rdo rje 'bar //
NK016(ma)006:49: zla btul 'bru sbas dril gsil zhing //
NK016(ma)006:50: 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la brten //
NK016(ma)006:52: 'bru bzhi sbas nas m+aum sgreng rtse mo dril gsil 'bar //
NK016(ma)006:54: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs gyis blta //
NK016(ma)006:57: zla btul 'bru sbas 'khril ba'i tshul gyis dzi na dzikra /
NK016(ma)006:58: 'bru bzhi l+aam sgreng rtse mor dril nyi ma 'bru
NK016(ma)006:59: lnga btud de 'dzum pa'i l+aam dwe sha ra ti
NK016(ma)006:60: / 'bru bzhi s+w+aa sgreng rtse mo rin chen 'bar //
NK016(ma)006:61: zla btul 'khril ba'i s+w+aa rat+na d+h+rika /
NK016(ma)006:62: 'bru bzhi m+aam sgreng rtse mor nyi ma btud de m+aam mo ha ra ti /
NK016(ma)006:64: zla btul 'khril ba'i +aam a ro lika /
NK016(ma)006:65: 'bru bzhi b+aam sgreng rtse mor nyi ma btud de p+aam ra ga ra ti /
NK016(ma)006:66: 'bru bzhi h+aa sgreng rtse mor ral gri 'bar //
NK016(ma)006:67: zla btul 'khril ba'i h+aa pra dz+nya d+h+rika /
NK016(ma)006:68: 'bru bzhi t+aam sgreng rtse mo nyi ma btud de
NK016(ma)006:69: t+aam badz+ra ra ti nang sems bzhi yi phyag rgya
NK016(ma)006:70: ni // rin chen myu gu ral gri 'bar //
NK016(ma)006:72: las la 'khril zhing chos la brten //
NK016(ma)006:73: nang sems yum gyi phyag rgya ni //
NK016(ma)006:74: gzugs mdzes rin chen phreng ba dang //
NK016(ma)006:75: pi wang gar mkhan mchog de nyid //
NK016(ma)006:77: pad+ma'i gdan la bzhengs nas kyang //
NK016(ma)006:78: mchod bzhes dam skongs dngos grub stsol //
NK016(ma)006:79: a la la hoh phyi sems bzhi yi phyag rgya ni //
NK016(ma)006:80: klu shing yal ga glegs bam dang //
NK016(ma)006:82: las la 'khril zhing phyi sems yum bzhi'i phyag rgya ni //
NK016(ma)006:83: me tog phreng dang spos mchod ma //
NK016(ma)006:84: mar me byug pa la sogs mdzin //
NK016(ma)006:86: pad+ma'i mchod bzhes a la la hoh thub drug phyag rgya sna tshogs te //
NK016(ma)006:87: mdor bsdus phyag rgya drug yin no //
NK016(ma)006:88: gseg par pi wang go cha dang //
NK016(ma)006:89: rin chen sgrom bu me chu 'dzin //
NK016(ma)006:90: pad+ma'i mchod bzhes a la la hoh sgo bzhi khro bo'i phyag rgya ni /
NK016(ma)006:91: n+ri mgo gdengs dang rdo rje gnon //
NK016(ma)006:92: thod sbrul chen por gnon pa dang //
NK016(ma)006:93: rdo rje rgya gram las kyis gnon //
NK016(ma)006:94: lcags kyu zhags pa s+pho ta hoh 'bar ba'i gdan
NK016(ma)006:95: la mchod bzhes a la la hoh 'di ni rgyal
NK016(ma)006:97: dgyes pa chen po bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK016(ma)006:98: phyag rgya'i mchod pa chen po yin //
NK016(ma)006:99: a la la ste mchod par 'bul //
NK016(ma)006:100: a la la ste dgyes par mdzod //
NK016(ma)006:101: gnyis pa khro bo'i phyag rgya la'ang spyi dang khyad par gnyis las /
NK016(ma)006:103: khrag 'thung rgyal po gar la dgyes //
NK016(ma)006:104: sku mdog zhal ni rnam par 'gyur //
NK016(ma)006:105: sku yi gar stabs glog 'gyu ba //
NK016(ma)006:106: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa 'bul //
NK016(ma)006:109: rnam par grol ba mtshon pa'i phyir //
NK016(ma)006:110: dbus kyi khro bo'i phyag rgya ni //
NK016(ma)006:111: mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa //
NK016(ma)006:112: g.yas pa rdo rje rtse lnga 'dzin //
NK016(ma)006:113: g.yon pa dung dmar yum la 'khyud //
NK016(ma)006:114: dpal chen che mchog thabs kyi rgya //
NK016(ma)006:115: gnam zhal dbyings phyug phyag rgya ni //
NK016(ma)006:116: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog mthing //
NK016(ma)006:117: g.yas pa shes rab thabs la brten //
NK016(ma)006:118: g.yon pa dung dmar gtso la stob //
NK016(ma)006:119: kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai dbyings kyi rgya //
NK016(ma)006:120: 'bar ba'i gdan la mchod bzhes a la la hoh rigs kyi khro bo'i phyag rgya las //
NK016(ma)006:121: badz+ra he ru ka'i phyag rgya ni //
NK016(ma)006:122: mthing nag rdo rje dung dmar 'dzin //
NK016(ma)006:123: dpal chen badz+ra thabs kyi rgya //
NK016(ma)006:124: bud+d+ha he ru ka'i phyag rgya ni //
NK016(ma)006:126: dpal chen bud+d+ha thabs kyi rgya //
NK016(ma)006:127: rat+na he ru ka'i phyag rgya ni //
NK016(ma)006:128: ser nag rin chen dung dmar 'dzin //
NK016(ma)006:129: dpal chen rat+na thabs pad+ma he ru ka'i phyag rgya ni //
NK016(ma)006:131: dpal chen pad+ma thabs karma he ru ka'i phyag rgya ni //
NK016(ma)006:132: ljang nag rgya gram dung dmar 'dzin //
NK016(ma)006:133: dpal chen karma thabs rak+sha he ru ka'i phyag rgya ni //
NK016(ma)006:134: mthing nag rdo rje dung dmar 'dzin //
NK016(ma)006:135: dpal chen rak+sha thabs sa nu he ru ka'i phyag rgya ni //
NK016(ma)006:136: ser nag dgra s+t+wa dung dmar 'dzin //
NK016(ma)006:137: dpal chen sa nu thabs gu h+ya he ru ka'i phyag rgya ni //
NK016(ma)006:138: dud kha ral gri dung dmar 'dzin //
NK016(ma)006:139: dpal chen gu h+ya thabs yak+sha he ru ka'i phyag rgya ni //
NK016(ma)006:140: ljang nag be con dung dmar 'dzin //
NK016(ma)006:141: dpal chen yak+sha thabs rigs kyi yum rnams phyag rgya ni //
NK016(ma)006:142: zhal gcig phyag gnyis rigs kyi mdog /
NK016(ma)006:143: g.yas pas shes rab thabs la brten //
NK016(ma)006:144: g.yon pas dung dmar gtso la stob //
NK016(ma)006:145: kro d+h+ai rigs rnams dbyings kyi rgya //
NK016(ma)006:146: 'bar ba'i mchod bzhes a la la hoh gnas ma brgyad kyi phyag rgya ni //
NK016(ma)006:147: koo r+ai b+han dmar zhing dbyug sngo //
NK016(ma)006:148: tsoo r+ai mda' gzhu 'gengs ma ser /
NK016(ma)006:149: pra mo chu srin rgyal mtshan dmar //
NK016(ma)006:150: be ta byis za rdor 'phyar nag /
NK016(ma)006:153: sma sha mthing nag byis snying za //
NK016(ma)006:155: 'bar ba'i mchod bzhes a la la hoh yul ma brgyad kyi phyag rgya ni //
NK016(ma)006:156: sid+ha kha ro bsnol ser seng //
NK016(ma)006:157: bya g+h+ri gnas blta bsnol mar stag /
NK016(ma)006:158: sri gal nag mo byis ldag wa //
NK016(ma)006:159: shwa na 'dral blta mthing ga spyang //
NK016(ma)006:160: g+h+ri d+d+ha mgrin dmar rgyu 'dren rgod //
NK016(ma)006:161: kang+ka kang phrag sna mgo ring //
NK016(ma)006:162: k+aa ka kha rog b+han gri nag /
NK016(ma)006:163: u l+au lcags kyu mthing tshogs 'ug /
NK016(ma)006:164: 'bar ba'i mchod bzhes a la la hoh sgo ma bzhi yi phyag rgya ni //
NK016(ma)006:165: rta gdong sngon mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK016(ma)006:166: phag gdong nag mo mche zhags can //
NK016(ma)006:167: seng gdong dmar mo lcags sgrog sdom //
NK016(ma)006:168: spyang gdong ljang nag dril 'khrol dgyes //
NK016(ma)006:169: 'bar ba'i mchod bzhes a la la hoh 'jig rten 'das dang ma 'das pa'i //
NK016(ma)006:170: ye shes thob par bya ba'i phyir //
NK016(ma)006:171: ma mo rnams kyi phyag rgya ni //
NK016(ma)006:172: srin mo smug nag thod rlon 'chang //
NK016(ma)006:173: tshangs pa dmar ser pad+ma bsnams //
NK016(ma)006:174: lha chen dkar ljang tri shu la //
NK016(ma)006:176: gzhon nu dmar mo mdung thung 'phen //
NK016(ma)006:177: brgya byin dkar mo in+d+ra gdengs //
NK016(ma)006:179: bdud rtsi dmar mo pad+ma bsnams //
NK016(ma)006:180: zla ba dkar mo pun+da ri //
NK016(ma)006:181: be con ljag nag dbyug to phyar //
NK016(ma)006:182: srin mo dmar mo dung khrag 'thung //
NK016(ma)006:183: za ba ljang nag ba su 'dren //
NK016(ma)006:184: dga' ba dmar mo ka dar phyar //
NK016(ma)006:185: stobs chen dkar mo gshol mda' 'dzin //
NK016(ma)006:186: rdo rje ser mo spu gris gcod //
NK016(ma)006:188: nor srung dmar mo bum pa 'dzin //
NK016(ma)006:189: rlung lha sngon mo ba dan phyar //
NK016(ma)006:190: gsod byed dkar mo ral gri 'dzin //
NK016(ma)006:191: ma mo dmar mo gsal shing phyar //
NK016(ma)006:192: phag gdong nag mo mche zhags can //
NK016(ma)006:193: rgan byed dmar mo zhing chung za //
NK016(ma)006:194: sna chen dkar ljang thod khrag 'thung //
NK016(ma)006:195: chu lha sngon mo sbrul zhags can //
NK016(ma)006:196: rdo rje nag mo lcags kyu 'dzin /
NK016(ma)006:197: rdo rje ser mo ra mgo zhags //
NK016(ma)006:198: rdo rje dmar mo lcags sgrog sdom //
NK016(ma)006:199: rdo rje ljang nag dril 'khrol dgyes //
NK016(ma)006:200: 'bar ba'i mchod bzhes a la la hoh 'di ni rgyal ba thams cad kun //
NK016(ma)006:201: dgyes pa chen po bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK016(ma)006:202: phyag rgya'i mchod pa chen po yin //
NK016(ma)006:203: a la la ste mchod par 'bul //
NK016(ma)006:204: a la la ste dgyes par mdzod //
NK016(ma)006:205: ces rim pa bzhin lha so so'i phyag rgya bya ba ste /
NK016(ma)006:206: de yang phyag rgya mdun du bsgyur nas yab g.yon dang yum g.yas su 'grol /
NK016(ma)006:207: de'i tshe lha gang dang gang gi sku sgyu ma lha bur gsal ba phyag chen /
NK016(ma)006:208: sa bon brjod pa chos rgya /
NK016(ma)006:210: dgrol ba las rgya ste phyag rgya bzhi'o //
NK016(ma)006:211: de yang ji skad du gsal bkra las /
NK016(ma)006:212: dam tshig las dang chos dang ni //
NK016(ma)006:213: sku nyid phyag rgya chen po'o //
NK016(ma)006:216: kun bzang sogs zhi ba dang /
NK016(ma)006:217: che mchog sogs khro bo so so'i bskyed sngags rnams
NK016(ma)006:218: gtso 'khor gyi 'gros sbyar te ji ltar rigs pa
NK016(ma)006:219: bzlas nas / zhes gsungs pa la bzlas pa'i grangs kyi bcu cha brtsi tshul ni /
NK016(ma)006:220: dper na bsnyen pa lta bu'i dus gtso bo kun bzang yab yum dang /
NK016(ma)006:221: che mchog yab yum rnams 'bum tsho re re tsam la /
NK016(ma)006:223: khro bo yab yum dgu la khri tsho re re tsam dang /
NK016(ma)006:224: sems dpa' brgyad la stong phrag lnga re /
NK016(ma)006:225: de phyin thams cad stong phrag re /
NK016(ma)006:226: zhi khro spyi sngags so sor chig 'bum tsam ste ci nus bazla'o //
NK016(ma)006:227: yang nyin chog rkyang pa lta bu'i skabs /
NK016(ma)006:229: che mchog yab yum brgya rtsa re /
NK016(ma)006:231: khro bo dgu sum cu re /
NK016(ma)006:232: sems dpa' brgyad nyi shu re /
NK016(ma)006:233: de phyin thams cad bcu phrag re /
NK016(ma)006:234: zhi khro spyi sngags ci nus re bzlas brjod bya'o //
NK016(ma)006:236: bzlas pa'i skabs kyi mjug bsdu'i bstod pa la /
NK016(ma)006:237: yang na zhi khro'i gzhi bstod gnyis sbrel nas bya
NK016(ma)006:238: zhing gsungs ba spro bar 'dod na de la gnyis
NK016(ma)006:243: chos nyid stong pa'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK016(ma)006:244: chos nyid kun tu bzang po 'du 'bral med //
NK016(ma)006:245: chos nyid khyab brdal chen po'i ye shes kyi //
NK016(ma)006:246: kun bzang yab yum gnyis la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK016(ma)006:247: rnam shes rnam dag bcom ldan rdo rje sems //
NK016(ma)006:248: zhe sdang rnam dag chos dbyings ye shes ngang //
NK016(ma)006:249: mthing ga phyag na rdo rje 'bar ba bsnams //
NK016(ma)006:250: thugs mchog rdo rje sems la phyag gzugs phung rnam dag bcom ldan rnam snang mdzad //
NK016(ma)006:251: gti mug rnam dag me long ye shes ngang //
NK016(ma)006:252: dung mdog phyag na 'khor lo 'bar ba bsnams //
NK016(ma)006:253: sku mchog rnams snang mdzad la phyag tshor ba rnam dag bcom ldan rin chen 'byung //
NK016(ma)006:254: nga rgyal rnam dag mnyam nyid ye shes ngang //
NK016(ma)006:255: gser mdog phyag na rin chen 'bar ba bsnams //
NK016(ma)006:256: yon tan rin chen 'byung la 'du shes rnam dag bcom ldan snang mtha' yas //
NK016(ma)006:257: 'dod chags rnam dag kun rtog ye shes ngang //
NK016(ma)006:258: le brgan phyag na pad+ma 'bar ba snams //
NK016(ma)006:259: gsung mchog snang mtha' yas la 'du byed rnam dag bcom ldan don yod grub //
NK016(ma)006:260: phrag dog rnam dag bya grub ye shes ngang //
NK016(ma)006:261: ljang gu phyag na ral gri 'bar ba bsnams //
NK016(ma)006:262: phrin las don yon grub la 'byung ba rnam dag rigs kyi yum chen lnga //
NK016(ma)006:263: kun bzang spyan ma m+aa k+ai gos dkar sgrol //
NK016(ma)006:264: thabs kyi sku la shes rab dgyes 'khril ma //
NK016(ma)006:265: rigs kyi yum chen lnga la phyag bskal bzang byang chub sems dpa' brgyad rnams ni //
NK016(ma)006:266: bde bar gshegs pa kun gyi sras mchog ste //
NK016(ma)006:267: yon tan mi zad sprul pa bsam yas pa'i //
NK016(ma)006:268: sems dpa' chen po brgyad la sgeg mo phreg thogs rin chen glu gar can //
NK016(ma)006:269: bdug pa me tog mar me dri chab ma //
NK016(ma)006:270: rgyal ba rgya mtsho rnams la mchod 'bul ma //
NK016(ma)006:271: mchod pa'i lha mo brgyad la ye shes sgo ba chen po yab yum brgyad //
NK016(ma)006:272: gshin rje stobs chen rta mgrin bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK016(ma)006:273: lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril bu ma //
NK016(ma)006:274: sgo ba yab yum brgyad la ye shes bzhi las rigs bzhi'i phrin las kyis //
NK016(ma)006:275: 'jig rten drug gi bye ba phrag brgya ru //
NK016(ma)006:276: sprul pa bye ba phrag brgyas 'gro drug gi //
NK016(ma)006:277: don mdzad thub pa drug la rgyal ba sras bcas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi //
NK016(ma)006:278: che ba'i yon tan brjod kyis mi lang yang //
NK016(ma)006:279: yon tan cha shas brjod pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK016(ma)006:280: rig 'dzin sngags 'chang rnal 'byor bdag cag gi //
NK016(ma)006:281: las dang nyon mongs bag chags gtan sbyangs nas //
NK016(ma)006:282: tshe 'di nyid la rig 'dzin sa thob ste //
NK016(ma)006:283: dpal ldan rdo rje sems dpa'i gnas thob shog /
NK016(ma)006:286: chos nyid mi 'gyur kun gzhi'i ye shes sku //
NK016(ma)006:287: ye shes gnas gyur che mchog he ru ka /
NK016(ma)006:288: stong nyid chos kyi dbyings phyug gnam zhal yum //
NK016(ma)006:289: che mchog he ru ka la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK016(ma)006:290: dus gsum mi 'gyur rnam shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK016(ma)006:291: zhe sdang mthar phyin badz+ra he ru ka /
NK016(ma)006:292: dbyings nas rgyas 'debs badz+ra khros pa'i yum //
NK016(ma)006:293: badz+ra he ru ka la ma 'gags rang gsal gzugs phung chos kyi sku //
NK016(ma)006:294: gti mug mthar phyin bud+ha he ru ka /
NK016(ma)006:295: dbyings nas rmongs sel bud+d+ha khros pa'i yum //
NK016(ma)006:296: bud+d+ha he ru ka la za byed gter tshogs tshor ba rin 'byung sku //
NK016(ma)006:297: nga rgyal mthar phyin rat+na he ru ka /
NK016(ma)006:298: dbyings nas tshe 'phel rat+na khros pa'i yum //
NK016(ma)006:299: rat+na he ru ka la chags med dag pa 'du shes pad+ma'i sku //
NK016(ma)006:300: 'dod chags mthar phyin pad+ma he ru ka /
NK016(ma)006:301: dbyings nas rdzogs byed pad+ma khros pa'i yum //
NK016(ma)006:302: pad+ma he ru ka la don rnams mthar phyin 'du byed sprul pa'i sku //
NK016(ma)006:303: phrag dog mthar phyin karma he ru ka /
NK016(ma)006:304: dbyings nas za byed karma khros pa'i yum //
NK016(ma)006:305: karma he ru ka la skye gnas rnam bzhi'i rtog pa gnas gyur sku //
NK016(ma)006:306: nyon mongs mthar phyin khrag 'thung rnam pa bzhi //
NK016(ma)006:307: dbyings nas 'dzin zhen 'joms mdzad dbyings phyug yum //
NK016(ma)006:308: he ru ka bzhi'i sku la 'jig rten bzhad pa'i dur khrod gnas brgyad nas //
NK016(ma)006:309: thugs mchog rnam dag ye shes dkar mo'i tshogs //
NK016(ma)006:310: thugs rje chen pos rnal 'byor grogs mdzad ma //
NK016(ma)006:311: gnas kyi koo r+ai brgyad la yon tan rtags kyi dur khrod gnas brgyad nas //
NK016(ma)006:312: 'jigs byed rtsal 'phags seng gdong phra men tshogs //
NK016(ma)006:313: thugs rje chen pos rnal 'byor grogs mdzad ma //
NK016(ma)006:314: yul gyi phra men brgyad la phyin ci log bzhi dur khrod gnas bzhi nas //
NK016(ma)006:315: tshad med bzhi yis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i //
NK016(ma)006:316: lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril bu ma //
NK016(ma)006:317: ye shes sgo ma bzhi la lha chen rnams kyi chung ma dbang mo'i tshogs //
NK016(ma)006:318: 'khor ba'i chos la mnga' brnyes srin mo'i gzugs //
NK016(ma)006:319: mya ngan 'das pa sprul sku mgo brnyan can //
NK016(ma)006:320: dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad la ye shes zhi ba'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK016(ma)006:321: gdug pa 'dul phyir 'bar ba'i skur ston pa //
NK016(ma)006:322: khrag 'thung rol pa'i lha tshogs lnga bcu brgyad //
NK016(ma)006:323: gdod nas ma skyes rang byung grub pa'i lha //
NK016(ma)006:324: tshe rabs sngon nas bsgrub pa'i 'phro mchis kyi //
